<p>This hands-on introduction to single Coptic stitch bookbinding is perfect for beginners and provides a solid foundation to inspire future projects. In this workshop, you will create your very own artistic and functional 4” x 6” notebook (approximately 80 pages). The notebook will lay flat when open and will feature an open-end (visible) binding allowing for a clear view of the spine as well as simple cover boards. Supplies are included in the cost of registration. Light refreshments will be served.</p>
